			<description><![CDATA[<div class="job" id="dev-ops-engineer">
<p>
ClaimAble is a mission-critical business application to our customers. Our reputation is built on accessibility and reliability, so it&#39;s important we maintain this.</p>
<p>
You&#39;ll be responsible for maintaining our platform infrastructure and making key architectural decisions about how to scale and ensure our application is always available.</p>
<p>
You&#39;ll also need to write Ruby code and be involved in the design of our API.</p>
</div>
<div class="section">
<p>
<u><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></u></p>
<ul>
<li>
Manage and maintain our platform infrastructure.</li>
<li>
We love RESTful JSON API&#39;s and you&#39;ll be responsible for designing and improving ours.</li>
<li>
Make architectural decisions about our entire back-end stack, from the network layer to the API.</li>
<li>
Ensure our platform is secure, resilient, performant and scalable.</li>
<li>
Write Ruby code for both our primary API and supporting applications.</li>
<li>
Automate as many processes as possible.</li>
<li>
Help us achieve rock solid failover across multiple data centres as our user base grows.</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="section">
<p>
<u><strong>You Must:</strong></u></p>
<ul>
<li>
Have real-life experience of cloud servers/infrastructure.</li>
<li>
Have demonstrable examples of applications you&#39;ve built and maintained (and scaled).</li>
<li>
Be passionate about startup culture - if you expect a 9-to-5, stop reading now.</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="section">
<p>
<u><strong>In A Typical Day You:</strong></u></p>
<ul>
<li>
Researched various hosting providers and advised the team who we should migrate to.</li>
<li>
Deployed a new version of the API.</li>
<li>
Setup a chatroom bot to automate future deploys.</li>
<li>
Hacked together a business dashboard showing key metrics for the team to monitor.</li>
<li>
Finished a small Sinatra application to display our platform status in realtime to users.</li>
<li>
Implemented DNS failover and load balancing as part of our expansion into multiple regions.</li>
<li>
Optimised some MongoDB queries to dramatically improve API performance.</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="section">
<p>
<u><strong>Bonus Points For:</strong></u></p>
<ul>
<li>
Experience with Chef scripts.</li>
<li>
Being familiar with MongoDB and how it scales.</li>
<li>
Having knowledge of web security/vulnerabilities and how to protect against them.</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="section">
<p>
<u><strong>Benefits &amp; Perks:</strong></u></p>
<ul>
<li>
A new Mac to work your magic on.</li>
<li>
A comfy Herman Miller Aeron chair.</li>
<li>
Office in vibrant Shoreditch, London surrounded by like-minded companies.</li>
<li>
ClaimAble is a bullshit free zone! You won&rsquo;t get dragged into pointless meetings or distracted from your work.</li>
<li>
Free food when you work late.</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="section">
<p>
<u><strong>Salary:</strong></u></p>
<p>
Salary is competitive and negotiable based on your experience.</p>
</div>
<p>
